# CyberQuest Architecture

## High-Level Flow

flowchart TD
    A[Participant enters profession/role] --> B[Personalization Layer<br/>Contextualizes scenarios to profession]
    B --> C[Assessment Engine<br/>Baseline 5]
    C --> D[Training Engine<br/>Storyline 10 + explanations]
    D --> E[Assessment Engine<br/>Reassessment 5]
    E --> F[Scoring Engine<br/>10 points correct, 0 incorrect]
    F --> G[Metrics<br/>Baseline, Storyline, Reassessment, Delta]
    G --> H[Reflection Engine<br/>Confidence + takeaway]
    H --> I[Participant records results externally]
